nodes.text: Wol Kessix was a male individual who served as an agent of the Resistance around the time of the Hosnian Cataclysm. After being sent to investigate the planet GH-531 in the Unknown Regions, Kessix crash-landed on the world and was imprisoned by the First Order within a secret communications facility that they operated on the planet. However, Kessix was later rescued by a group of Resistance-aligned adventurers who had ventured to the communications facility on a mission to seize communications data from the base.
